archimate:BusinessFunction.name: MULTIDISCIPLINAIRE SAMENWERKING
archimate:BusinessFunction.documentation: <languages xml:space="preserve"><nl-NL>Samenwerking tussen meerdere specialistische disciplines ihkv passende zorg en netwerkzorg. Kan plaatsvinden in meerdere echelons en daarmee zowel intra- als transmuraal.</nl-NL><en-US>Collaboration between multiple specialist disciplines in connection with appropriate care and network care. Can take place in multiple echelons and therefore both intramural and transmural. </en-US></languages>
